The blog post attached is the experience of an experienced engineer who states he was interviewed by Google for a SW dev. manager position. 
It is interesting for two reasons:
1) The recruiter was clearly not qualified.
2) At the end of the article, he speculates (with proof) that google hired an internet shill (aka لجان الكترونية) to try and maliciously kill the page rank.

Edit: this is the same link published here earlier by Karim Mohamed, but the blog post below contains more details than the BI article.
